#: ../../user_manual/ekos-focus.rst:1977
msgid ""
"``Optimise Tile Centres``: If unchecked, the geometrical centre of the tile "
"is used; if checked, the centre of the tile is calculated as an average of "
"the star positions within the tile. Whilst theoretically more accurate to "
