#: ../../user_manual/ekos-focus.rst:2040
msgid ""
"``Num Stars``: This shows the min / max number of stars detected during the "
"Autofocus run. Usually, the minimum number would be a far out of focus "
"datapoint and the max number would be the in focus datapoint."
